<p>5. Apple air tags</p>



<p>6. Journal and pen.&nbsp;I like <a href="https://amzn.to/48UEPtv" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">these journals in Lochby covers</a>.</p>



<p>7. Buff / Neck gaiter. <a href="https://amzn.to/4qvE2W6" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">I like this one</a>, but there are hundreds of different kinds.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>



