<p>10. Clif Bars, preferably the <a href="https://amzn.to/4qwdrrM" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">crunchy peanut butter flavour.</a></p>



<p>11. 2-Battery USB-C charger</p>



<p>12. Small binoculars, <a href="https://amzn.to/3J7oPK9" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">mine are Leica Trinovid 8&#215;20</a></p>



<p>13. <a href="https://amzn.to/3JtkDEy" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Rick Young Outdoors Harness</a>&nbsp;</p>



